Package Model

package Model
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    Admin
    The Admin class represents an administrator in the system, inheriting from the Staff class.
    Appointment
    The Appointment class represents a scheduled meeting between a Patient and a Doctor.
    AppointmentList
    The AppointmentList class is a singleton that manages the list of appointments in the application.
    AppointmentOutcome
    The AppointmentOutcome class represents the outcome of a medical appointment, including prescribed medicines, diagnoses, services provided, and payment status.
    Diagnosis
    The Diagnosis class represents a medical diagnosis for a patient.
    Doctor
    Represents a doctor in the hospital management system.
    InventoryList
    The InventoryList class represents an inventory item in the medical inventory system.
    MedicalRecord
    Represents the medical record of a patient in the hospital management system.
    Medicine
     
    Patient
    Represents a patient in the hospital management system.
    Pharmacist
    The Pharmacist class represents a specific type of Staff member in the hospital management system.
    ReplenishmentRequest
    The ReplenishmentRequest class represents a request to replenish stock levels for a specific medicine.
    Schedule
    Represents a schedule with a specific start time and end time.
    Specialization
    Represents a specialization in a particular medical field or expertise.
    Staff
    The Staff class represents an employee in a hospital management system.
    Treatment
    Represents a medical treatment associated with a diagnosis.
